(hfy-parse-tags-buffer @var{srcdir} @var{buffer})
@end lisp

Parse a @var{buffer} containing etags formatted output, loading the
@ref{hfy-tags-cache} and @ref{hfy-tags-sortl} entries for @var{srcdir}.

@item hfy-interq
@findex hfy-interq
@anchor{hfy-interq}

