(hfy-interq @var{set-a} @var{set-b})
@end lisp

Return the intersection (using @code{eq}) of 2 lists.

@item hfy-text-p
@findex hfy-text-p
@anchor{hfy-text-p}

@lisp

(hfy-text-p @var{srcdir} @var{file})
@end lisp

Is @var{srcdir}/@var{file} text?  Uses @ref{hfy-istext-command} to determine this.

@item hfy-opt
